To build and install libslablist, you'll need to do the following.

On Illumos[1] based systems:
	cd build/
	./build_install_illumos

On Unix[2] systems (i.e. those without umem):
	cd build/
	./build_install_unix

To uninstall:
	./remove_lib

To clean the build directory
	./clean_lib; ./clean_drv;

[1]: So far has only been tested on OpenIndiana and SmartOS.
[2]: Hasn't been tested recently
